Hubert RILEY, Appellee, v. THE Barge JAMES MORIARITY, James Moriarity, Appellant. No. 431. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 29, 1933. Thomas A. McDonald, of New York City (Franklin M. Depew, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Burke & Desmond, of Buffalo, N. Y. (Charles S. Desmond, of Buffalo, N. Y., of counsel), for appellee.

Before MANTON, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed.
